Title: Duane Barry (1)
Plot: Mulder is called to a hostage situation involving Duane Barry, a former FBI Agent who claims to be an alien abductee and wants to get back to the abduction site with someone who will be taken instead of him. Unfortunately, the someone he eventually chooses is Scully.
GuestStars: Steve Railsback, Nicholas Lea, Frank C. Turner, Fred Henderson, Stephen E. Miller, Barbara Pollard, Sarah Strange, Robert Lewis, Tosca Baggoo, Tim Dixon, Prince Maryland, John Sampson, Michael Dobson, CCH Pounder
